I moved to Palermo for studying language; I left the town where i was  born and  lived for about 18 years, I met a lotta of folks and even people i would like to forget i got to know. Anyway, after all I didn't let life change me because if i remain confident that if you do so you're going to get worse and ,of course, you won't live a kind of life you truly like. I achieved just a small part of my goals and, speaking personally, if i continue fighting the way I do now everything is gonna be the way I want. #happymoments #newyearsparty2018 #newgoals
